@startuml
title Interaction Design - Chat to Agent Response
skinparam shadowing false

actor User
participant "Frontend Chat Page" as FE
participant "FastAPI /api/chat" as API
participant "Orchestrator" as ORCH
participant "Agent" as AGENT
participant "ProfileMemoryService" as MEM
database "SQLite DB" as DB
participant "LLM API" as LLM

User -> FE : Submit message
FE -> API : POST /api/chat
API -> DB : Load recent messages + profile
API -> ORCH : route_and_execute(input, context)
ORCH -> AGENT : process(...)
AGENT -> LLM : generate structured output
LLM --> AGENT : response payload
AGENT --> ORCH : classified items + reply
ORCH --> API : normalized response
API -> MEM : extract memory candidates
MEM -> LLM : extract/update profile facts
LLM --> MEM : memory candidates
MEM -> DB : save profile_update + user_context
API -> DB : save user/assistant messages
API --> FE : AgentChatResponse
FE --> User : Render message, items, schedule/reflection
@enduml
